{"tid":1553361,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【團結】無大台嘅抗爭，我哋應該無時無刻激烈咁互屌。但冷靜之後要記得我哋係同路人","createTime":"2019-09-08T14:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:25:45.000Z","uid":66260,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"220f98c55b7f5ca4d38da766b55ff9688c522b04","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305309/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305309/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n反送中運動由開始直到現在，抗爭路線同手法一路經歷過好大分歧<br />\n例如地鐵不合作運動、圍警總定散水、搞稅局有冇用、九龍遊行後去唔去旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中有做得好、有做得唔好嘅地方，香港人一直都喺過程中學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但有唔同意見嘅時候，民陣、泛民、黃之峰、楊逸朗、衝擊立法會嘅死士、部份連登仔都被人話過係鬼，係入嚟破壞呢場運動。到呢一刻佢哋係唔係鬼大家自行判斷<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但團結先係我哋最大嘅本錢</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n香港人用咗廿年時間終於學識單靠和理非、或者勇武其中一方係無可能成功<br />\n如果輕易話人係鬼，用誅心論，和理非同勇武唔會合作，我哋唔會有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次無大台帶領，我哋互屌係正常嘅，係必要嘅<br />\n應該無時無刻咁屌激烈咁屌，屌到天昏地暗山崩地裂<br />\n因為只有經得起挑戰嘅想法先有價值 &quot;The unexamined idea is not worth actualizing&quot;<br />\n但只限於屌想法，唔係人身攻擊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>唯有團結一致，不分化不割席我哋先有勝利嘅希望<br />\n希望大家唔好忘記初心</ins><br />\n<br />\n最後引用一句毛澤東嘅語錄<br />\n「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要分清敵我，不能站在敵對的立場用對待敵人的態度來對待同志。必須是滿腔熱情地用保護人民事業和提高人民覺悟的態度來說話，而不能用嘲笑和攻擊的態度來說話。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYkTBz9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYkTBz9.jpg&h=3e94573e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"094062c5c8c4ba19d72ffafe846620da7fc265d2","tid":1553361,"uid":315851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:50:15.000Z","msg":"提防六大害<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1552553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1552553</a>"},{"pid":"a5f7614d63c2ef440c9fdbf88862c6750ec579a9","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"舊post重開, 希望大家繼續激烈互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但請大家記住, <span style=\"color: red;\">今日屌完今日散, 大家手足冇隔夜仇</span><br />\n檢討完之後就一齊學下點樣下次做好啲</span>"},{"pid":"ff414e5209b9952cb39bec38d9e1001c10ba127d","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354e6365ad68251cbd98e7f47c75468a60c9bac7","tid":1553361,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:53:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />激烈的海膽"},{"pid":"ecfb0202a67af8f222351246d83773af2b25fe99","tid":1553361,"uid":49898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:53:46.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n咁樣先係我地想追求嘅社會"},{"pid":"0deb4151531700dc48eee66c30dbb19156392803","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e5e6b0d5e11a194156793bfb4a3327a184caf6","tid":1553361,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"講得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂互屌到出野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（worth acutalizing idea)"},{"pid":"09cc10566e598400d854a121a6e5d258c915fb1c","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b31aa48aa85f6fe8cccb3640c63c45b5ec6f4f","tid":1553361,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"要做到同接受到和而不同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6ab4dfeb0bc7184ffe43e661c775e9a818948a","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c38defea18d7b15bb06ed8ab71adaa74fe83a4","tid":1553361,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba421f7e62ac161cd94b1bdc67cb87f4d29e6e64","tid":1553361,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:00:26.000Z","msg":"要檢討係玩laser問題 傷唔到狗一條毛 又俾狗有位入 圍狗屋/勇武前線都算 好似美領依種合家歡和理非大會 就忍忍手"},{"pid":"233a6d3bcc71456b006e6cb08f1b4f44b0411ef0","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d63673debe405bc0cf48d1a6fed7a0916bfc84b","tid":1553361,"uid":147785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<br />\n屌無問題 只要記住<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"eeccb4a68a5a38ab762a0539294fa7b6f05848b6","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2149da880c30981ef0ccd38d34238c8c7b046749","tid":1553361,"uid":290836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ce53525ebd326d8b89b8e9661c35bb0326ef382","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae964ea452206dc9b5a76a9a450af242ed4a9d4","tid":1553361,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71b6b5c92059340066c04aaa21882023d1fd4ef","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47dc4850724efaa28b68fe31ca74f3ba763c25a4","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c124c997de920ab25a77a2466353b3a17cadee1","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b0be3353bf063f68674ed67c96ab2786f25fa0","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4274f12ee4f1634f5d9767f5f6b06fb93a547a14","tid":1553361,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}